---
title: Mexican-Style Double Salmon and Rice Bowls with Tomato-Cucumber Salsa
description: For a scrumptious meal with a bit of Mexican flair, look no further. Juicy salmon is seasoned with Mexican seasoning and is nestled atop a steaming bed of zesty cilantro rice. A  sprinkling of feta and drizzling of zippy sour cream-lime sauce dressing ties everything together for the perfect bite.
